ates. Credit: Jack Dallas-Chapman" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates.-Credit-Jack-Dallas-Chapman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Billy-Nomates">Billy Nomates</a> has announced her new album &#39;Metalhorse&#39; and shared the rebellious single &#39;The Test&#39;.在下面查看。</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/billy-nomates-interview-2023-cacti-3377120">Billy Nomates: “I&#39;m a woman in the modern world, of course I&#39;m angry!”</a></strong></li></ul><p> &#39;The Test&#39; features a low humming bass and bright piano interjections which are paired with Nomates&#39; – real name Tor Maries – powerful vocal lines.她唱着： <em>“镜子大厅 /我做死亡的墙 /我无所畏惧 /当我付房租时。”</em></p><p>这首歌是为即将发行的专辑写的第一首曲目，并在新闻稿中被描述为“过去18个月的动荡，而比利提名人仍在继续进行的令人困惑的曲目。</p><p> Maries described it as: “It&#39;s working at something against the odds and feeling like someone&#39;s helping you from the other side, and if they see you that&#39;s the test. I really feel that when we&#39;re playing it live. Like, with everything that&#39;s going on, I can&#39;t believe this is surviving.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Billy Nomates - The Test (official visualiser)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BxMrKNp0Tr0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> &#39;Metalhorse&#39; is set for release on May 16 via Invada and is available for pre-order <a href="http://lnk.to/metalhorse" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> . It follows her 2023 LP &#39;CACTI&#39; and her 2020 self-titled debut.</p><p> Produced by James Trevascus and recorded at Paco Loco in Seville, Spain, &#39;Metalhorse&#39; is Maries&#39; first album to be created in a studio with a full band.新闻稿承诺将其成为“ Fuller专辑”，并看到音乐家探索新的流派，例如布鲁斯，民间和钢琴驱动的安排，将她通常的Stark Punk声音转变为更卑鄙的东西。</p><p> Maries&#39; and the full band – comprised of bass player Mandy Clarke ( <a href="/artists/kt-tunstall">KT Tunstall</a> , The Go! Team) and drummer Liam Chapman (Rozi Plain, BMX Bandits) – took to the studio shortly after the passing of her father.</p><p>玛丽斯在谈到她与父亲的关系时说：“我们是如此亲密，我们的纽带是音乐。那是我在世界上的安全和保护。 Even in the care home, as things were getting worse, I&#39;d visit him and he&#39;d ask me what I was doing. I&#39;d show him the new demos, or I&#39;d have been on the radio.这有点拯救了一切，因为我们有这个积极的事情要谈论。” </p><figure id="attachment_3844225" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3844225" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3844225" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Billy Nomates &#39;Metalhorse&#39; album artwork.信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Billy-Nomates-Metalhorse-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3844225" class="wp-caption-text"> Billy Nomates &#39;Metalhorse&#39; album artwork.信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>The &#39;Metalhorse&#39; Tracklist is:</strong></h2><p> <strong>1. &#39;Metalhorse&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2. &#39;Nothing Worth Winning&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>3. &#39;The Test&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4. &#39;Override&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5. &#39;Dark Horse Friend feat. Hugh Cornwell&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>6. &#39;Life&#39;s Unfair&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>7. &#39;Plans&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>8. &#39;Gas&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>9. &#39;Comedic Timing&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>10. &#39;Strange Gift&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>11. &#39;Moon Explodes&#39;</strong></p><p> LP被描述为一张概念专辑，涉及有关生活的动荡 - 风险和愉悦，危险和振奋的主题。 “To me, &#39;Metalhorse&#39; is this crumbling fairground where some rides are nice to get on and some rides aren&#39;t. That&#39;s how life felt for a minute, and it still feels like that a bit now,” Maries explained.</p><p>她继续说：“那些<a href="/artists/leonard-cohen">伦纳德·科恩（Leonard Cohen）的</a>日子可能比我领先。 but for now there has to be some hope, even if it&#39;s not real. You have to tell someone that it&#39;s going to be alright.”</p><p>在其他地方，比利的提名人士将在店内演出一系列专辑发行周以及本月晚些时候和四月的少数现场约会。在下面查看巡回演出的完整列表，然后访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbilly-nomates-tickets%2Fartist%2F5342572" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。</p><h2><strong>比利提名2025 Live和店​​内的巡回演出日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>6  - 法国巴黎的莱斯河畔节 - 独奏</strong><br /><strong>29  - 英国布里斯托尔的仪式联盟节标题 - 完整乐队</strong></p><p><strong>四月</strong><br /><strong>5  -  CRO CRO土地节标题，英国伦敦克罗伊登 - 独奏</strong></p><p><strong>五月（店内）</strong><br /> <strong>18  - 英国诺丁汉的粗糙贸易</strong><br /><strong>19  - 英国伦敦的粗糙贸易东部</strong><br /><strong>20  - 英国布莱顿居民</strong><br /><strong>22  - 英国考文垂刚赶到</strong></p><p>The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-nomates-announces-third-album-metalhorse-rebellious-new-single-the-test-3844195">Billy Nomates announces third album &#39;Metalhorse&#39; with rebellious new single &#39;The Test&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
